name: Active member ships
query:
SELECT
    gym_member_name AS "Gym Member::160",
    Membership_plan_name AS "Membership Plan::150",
    start_date AS "Start Date:Date:160",
    end_date AS "End Date:Date:160",
    status AS "Status::160",
    invoice AS "Sales Invoice:Link/Sales Invoice:260",
    payment_status AS "Payment Status::160"
FROM
    `tabMembership`
WHERE
    status = 'Active'
ORDER BY
    end_date ASC;
